PCQuest - September 2014  IN

92 Pages | True PDF | English | 13 MB 

PCQuest is the second oldest IT publication in the country of India.  It's positioned in the enterprise IT implementation space and helps key IT decision makers to understand technologies, choose the right products and solutions, and implement the right IT solutions. PCQuest is ranked as the number one magazine by IT purchase decision makers across the country in helping them with their IT purchases. Established in 1987, PCQuest (earlier PC World India), is the fastest growing infotech monthly in India
